<subSubSection id="C36696BB8E5FFFB2FF1AFA2BDA27F9C6" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BC3C5308E5FFFB2FF1AFA2BDA27F9C6" blockId="4.[163,1070,1488,1568]" pageId="4" pageNumber="145">
Comment: The vast distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7CBEB38E5FFFB2FDCDFA2BDA79FA00" baseAuthorityName="MOTSCHULSKY" baseAuthorityYear="1858" box="[628,772,1488,1510]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Gabronthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maritimus">
<emphasis id="B90819228E5FFFB2FDCDFA2BDA79FA00" box="[628,772,1488,1510]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="145">G. maritimus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
includes the Afrotropical, Palaearctic, and 
<collectingRegion id="49B80BD28E5FFFB2FEEAFA16D8DBF9E5" box="[339,422,1517,1539]" country="Saudi Arabia" name="Ash Sharqiyah" pageId="4" pageNumber="145">Oriental</collectingRegion>
regions (
<bibRefCitation id="EFEDB8C18E5FFFB2FDB6FA16DBC8F9E5" author="SMETANA A" box="[527,693,1517,1539]" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" pagination="505 - 698" refId="ref7869" refString="SMETANA A. (2004): Staphylinidae, subfamilies Omaliinae - Dasycerinae, Phloeocharinae - Apaticinae, Piestinae - Staphylininae, pp. 237 - 272, 329 - 495, 505 - 698. - In: LOBL I. &amp; A. SMETANA (eds), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. II. Hydrophiloidea - Histeroidea - Staphylinoidea. - Stenstrup, Apollo Books: 942 pp." type="book chapter" year="2004">SMETANA 2004</bibRefCitation>
). The species had already been reported from 
<collectingCountry id="F36B85A08E5FFFB2FE98F9F1D8DBF9C6" box="[289,422,1546,1568]" name="Saudi Arabia" pageId="4" pageNumber="145">Saudi Arabia</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFEDB8C18E5FFFB2FE74F9F1DB09F9C6" author="COIFFAIT H" box="[461,628,1546,1568]" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" pagination="236 - 242" refId="ref7460" refString="COIFFAIT H. (1981): Insects of Saudi Arabia. Coleoptera: Fam. Staphylinidae, Subfam. Xantholininae, Staphylininae, Paederinae, Oxytelinae, Aleocharinae (Part 2). - Fauna of Saudi Arabia 3: 236 - 242." type="journal article" year="1981">COIFFAIT (1981)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFEDB8C18E5FFFB2FD1CF9F1DA2AF9C6" author="GUSAROV V" box="[677,855,1546,1568]" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" pagination="277 - 290" refId="ref7600" refString="GUSAROV V. I. (1997): Staphylinids (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae) from Saudi Arabia and Oman. - Fauna of Saudi Arabia 16: 277 - 290." type="journal article" year="1997">GUSAROV (1997)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
